item.title: How Well do Political Parties Satisfy their Voters?
item.description: Abstract This paper analyzes the most important things to voters of the; Liberal, Conservative, and NDP political parties in Canada and compares them to what these political parties promise to accomplish if elected. FOUND FOUND FOUND FOUND FOUND FOUND FOUND FOUND FOUND FOUND FOUND FOUND This study is significant as voter satisfaction is extremely important in keeping elected parties in office for future terms.
